# Tag Salon

Tag Salon is a mobile application that allows users to find nearby salons, view ratings, and book appointments بسهولة.

## Features
- Nearby salon search using location
- Distance calculation with maps
- Rating-based salon recommendations
- Appointment booking

## Tech Stack
- Android (Kotlin/Java)
- Google Maps API
- Firebase

## Future Improvements
- Online payments
- Reviews & feedback system
